# Table Look & Feel Specification (Source of Truth)

## Overall Style
- Modern SaaS admin dashboard
- Clean, light, spacious, neutral
- White surfaces on light grey background
- Subtle borders, soft shadows, rounded corners
- No visual clutter, strong alignment, generous spacing

## Table Container
- Table must be wrapped in a **Card**
- Card styles:
  - Background: white
  - Border: 1px solid light neutral
  - Border radius: 12px
  - Padding: 0 (table handles internal spacing)
  - Optional subtle shadow (very light, low elevation)

## Table Layout
- Full-width table
- Fixed header row
- Clear column alignment
- No vertical grid lines
- Very subtle horizontal row dividers

## Header Row
- Background: very light neutral (slightly darker than page background)
- Text:
  - Font size: 13–14px
  - Font weight: 600
  - Color: muted dark grey
  - Upper/lowercase: normal (not all caps)
- Height: ~48px
- Padding: 16px horizontal
- Checkbox column aligned left with consistent spacing

## Body Rows
- Row height: ~56px
- Padding:
  - 16px horizontal
  - Vertically centered content
- Text:
  - Primary text: 14–15px, medium weight
  - Secondary text (email, meta): muted color
- Hover state:
  - Very subtle background highlight
  - No borders added on hover

## Row Dividers
- Horizontal separators only
- Color: very light neutral
- Thickness: 1px
- No zebra striping

## Checkbox Column
- Small, minimal checkbox
- Aligned vertically center
- Slight left padding from table edge
- Checkbox should not dominate visually

## Status Badge / Pill
- Rounded pill shape
- Soft background color
- No hard borders
- Padding: small horizontal + vertical
- Font size: ~12–13px
- Font weight: 500

Status color rules:
- Active: soft green background, darker green text
- Pending: soft yellow background, darker yellow/orange text
- Inactive: soft grey background, muted text

## Numeric Columns (e.g. Balance)
- Right-aligned
- Use tabular/monospaced numerals if available
- Currency symbol included
- Same font size as body text
- Slightly higher contrast than secondary text

## Actions Column
- Right-aligned
- Uses **icon buttons only**
- Icons:
  - Edit
  - Delete
  - Overflow (three dots)
- Icon buttons:
  - Neutral color by default
  - Subtle hover background
  - No visible borders
- No text labels in the table row
- Tooltips on hover for accessibility

## Toolbar / Table Header Actions
- Appears above the table inside the card
- Contains:
  - Primary or secondary action button (e.g. “Export to CSV”)
- Button style:
  - Rounded corners
  - Clear primary color
  - Icon + label
- Toolbar aligned to the right

## Footer / Pagination
- Appears below the table inside the card
- Contains:
  - Rows per page selector
  - Item count (e.g. “1–5 of 8”)
  - Page navigation arrows
- Footer text:
  - Small, muted
- Pagination controls minimal and unobtrusive

## Spacing & Density Rules
- Prioritise readability over density
- Avoid tight or cramped rows
- Consistent spacing across all tables
- Tables should feel “calm” and easy to scan

## Do Not
- Do not use heavy borders
- Do not use bright or saturated colors
- Do not use text links for row actions
- Do not add unnecessary icons
- Do not use zebra striping

## Cursor Instruction (recommended)
Apply the table look and feel defined in this file.
Do not change functionality or data.
Only adjust layout, spacing, typography, colors, and component structure to match the spec exactly.
